OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775721946
OL,3,CHospice could close 'if funding crisis
OL,4,Ccontinues'
OL,6,FA hospice could be forced to close in
OL,7,Fjust 18 months time if its financial
OL,8,Fcrisis continues, it has said.
OL,10,FQueenscourt Hospice, in Southport,
OL,11,Fannounced it is halving the number of
OL,12,Fin-patient beds available to five to
OL,13,Ftry and help with the financial
OL,14,Fpressures, after operating with a #2
OL,15,Fmillion deficit for the past two years.
OL,17,FDr Clare Finnegan, Executive Medical
OL,18,FDirector, said: "If we do not take
OL,19,Fmeasures to cut our costs, Queenscourt
OL,20,Fwill be forced to close.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
