OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775721946
OL,3,CHospice could close 'if funding crisis
OL,4,Ccontinues'
OL,6,F"This is not an outcome the charity is
OL,7,Fwilling to accept, and we must now
OL,8,Ftake urgent action if Queenscourt is
OL,9,Fto survive."
OL,11,FThe hospice also announced it is being
OL,12,Fforced to reduce some of its wider
OL,13,Fcore clinical services including at
OL,14,Fhome shifts and outpatient therapy
OL,15,Fservices, in addition to housekeeping
OL,16,Fand catering services.
OL,18,FThe charity has launched a fundraising
OL,19,Fcampaign to protect the future of the
OL,20,Fhospice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
