PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775721946
OL,3,CHospice could close 'if funding crisis
OL,4,Ccontinues'
OL,6,F"The support we've already seen from
OL,7,Four community has been incredible, but
OL,8,Fwe urgently need more help," Dr
OL,9,FFinnegan said.
OL,11,FQueenscourt has been running for 35
OL,12,Fyears, caring for patients from across
OL,13,FWest Lancashire, Formby and Southport.
OL,15,FIn 2025 just 24% of its funding came
OL,16,Ffrom the NHS, with the hospice relying
OL,17,Fon short-term grants, fundraising and
OL,18,Fpersonal donations to meet the
OL,19,Fremaining cost of its services.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
