CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775721946
OL,3,CHospice could close 'if funding crisis
OL,4,Ccontinues'
OL,6,FHowever as salaries rise, alongside an
OL,7,Fincrease in energy bills and National
OL,8,FInsurance contributions their deficit
OL,9,Fhas worsened.
OL,11,FThe hospice has been asking the
OL,12,Fintegrated care boards of Lancashire,
OL,13,FSouth Cumbria, Cheshire and Merseyside
OL,14,Fto increase their contributions to 35-
OL,15,F40%.
OL,17,F"However we have been advised that we
OL,18,Fwill not receive this level of funding
OL,19,Funtil 2029," Dr Finnegan said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
