OL,3,CHospice could close 'if funding crisis
OL,4,Ccontinues'
OL,6,FCharlie King, Director of External
OL,7,FAffairs at Hospice UK said: "This is
OL,8,Fan incredibly difficult time for
OL,9,Feveryone at Queenscourt Hospice, and
OL,10,Four thoughts are with the staff
OL,11,Faffected, as well as the patients and
OL,12,Ffamilies who rely on their care.
OL,14,F"Sadly, this is not an isolated
OL,15,Fsituation. Hospices across the UK are
OL,16,Ffacing growing financial pressures,
OL,17,Fwith 6 out of 10 hospices either
OL,18,Fmaking cuts or planning to....
OL,26,@oD@]OU
