OL,3,CHospice could close 'if funding crisis
OL,4,Ccontinues'
OL,6,F"We can all agree that pain relief,
OL,7,Fmedications and the salaries of nurses
OL,8,Fand other healthcare staff shouldn't
OL,9,Fhave to rely on bake sales, fun runs
OL,10,Fand the sale of second hand clothes."
